@node mowersim "What is 'mowersim.lha'?"
@{u}mowersim.lha@{uu}

This is the biggest and best collection of lawnmower simulators ever!

As well as als.library, it also contains other Amiga versions (full screen original, enhanced ALS+ etc), a Casio calculator version, Acorn and Flex/MSX etc emulator versions.

Download it now! - Aminet game/misc/mowersim.lha

Update: There are some additional and/or updated ALS versions available from
http://www.unsatisfactory.freeserve.co.uk/als/download/

@endnode

